        <h2>
            古代世界历史地图集的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 2 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8329916">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8329916/" class="title-link">关于该书正确的使用方法</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8329916"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/157173968/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u157173968-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/157173968/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Max</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-02-01"
      class="main-meta">2017-02-01 22:48:46</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8329916_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  古代世界地图没有翻译是巨大的不足且被读者所诟病，不搞学术没有几个人受得了，出版社的理由太过敷衍。根本就是修图成本太高吧！这时你手边需要一本泰晤士世界历史地图册作为参考书拯救你。 实事求是的说两部书关于欧洲古代历史的备注说明还是挺有趣的补充与对照。对有兴趣的历...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/8329916/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
